1. *Šanse* da će uspeti su veoma male. (The chances of success are very slim.)
2. *Šansa* da će dobiti nagradu je veoma mala. (The chance of winning the prize is very small.)
3. Oni su dobili svoju *šansu* i oni je iskoristili. (They were given their chance and they took it.)
4. Oni će imati *šansu* da pokažu svoje veštine. (They will have a chance to show their skills.)
5. Ona je dobila *šansu* da dokaže svoju inteligenciju. (She was given a chance to prove her intelligence.)
6. Oni će imati priliku da dobiju *šansu* da se iskažu. (They will have the opportunity to get a chance to show themselves.)